articles.title: Facebook founder Mark Zuckerberg wins medals on jiu-jitsu debut - The Guardian
articles.description: Tech billionaire, 38, surprises onlookers by winning gold and silver medal at tournament in Redwood City, California
articles.content:
Mark Zuckerberg is adding one more title to his résumé: medal-winning martial artist.
